WEBVTT

00:02.052 --> 00:05.501
Lake Baikal is one of the oldest lakes in the world.

00:06.207 --> 00:09.594
It is located in the very heart of the largest continent,...

00:09.727 --> 00:13.237
...in a rift valley between two tectonic plates.

00:14.005 --> 00:19.125
There is a theory that Lake Baikal is on its way to becoming an ocean basin.

00:20.742 --> 00:25.862
Here, the steppes are gradually replaced by Siberian boreal forests.

00:26.057 --> 00:29.877
The mountain ranges form diverse landscapes of forests,...

00:30.099 --> 00:32.711
...alpine meadows and alpine tundra.

00:34.193 --> 00:40.305
This is the land of crystal clear lakes, clean rivers and magnificent waterfalls.

